        // 1\n                                                                                                           // 2\n/**                                                                                                        // 3\n * Convenience functions for use on client.                                                                // 4\n *                                                                                                         // 5\n * NOTE: You must restrict user actions on the server-side; any                                            // 6\n * client-side checks are strictly for convenience and must not be                                         // 7\n * trusted.                                                                                                // 8\n *                                                                                                         // 9\n * @module UIHelpers                                                                                       // 10\n */                                                                                                        // 11\n                                                                                                           // 12\nvar _registerHelper                                                                                        // 13\n                                                                                                           // 14\n////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////                                               // 15\n// UI helpers                                                                                              // 16\n//                                                                                                         // 17\n// Use a semi-private variable rather than declaring UI                                                    // 18\n// helpers directly so that we can unit test the helpers